WEBVTT

00:04:59.500 --> 00:05:01.333
What's the point? Nobody listens."

00:05:02.375 --> 00:05:04.184
Educated women said

00:05:04.208 --> 00:05:05.768
that their number one problem

00:05:05.792 --> 00:05:09.059
was their inability to speak up,

00:05:09.083 --> 00:05:11.976
as if there was a foot on their throat

00:05:12.000 --> 00:05:13.250
ready to choke them.

00:05:14.250 --> 00:05:17.208
Silence slices off women.

00:05:19.375 --> 00:05:22.268
Habit three: Be a people pleaser.

00:05:22.292 --> 00:05:23.559
Please others.

00:05:23.583 --> 00:05:26.726
Everyone likes a nice woman
who always smiles,

00:05:26.750 --> 00:05:29.184
who never says no, who is never angry,

00:05:29.208 --> 00:05:31.268
even when she's being exploited.